<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 18:16:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，欧洲顶级干邑生产商将出席中国反倾销调查会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/europes-top-cognac-makers-will-attend-china-meeting-anti-dumping-probe-source-2024-07-05/</link><description>一位业内消息人士称，欧洲主要干邑白兰地生产商将于 7 月 18 日在北京出席中国对该行业反倾销调查的听证会，这是自今年早些时候调查开始以来，他们第一次有机会亲自为自己辩护。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 12:26:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/europes-top-cognac-makers-will-attend-china-meeting-anti-dumping-probe-source-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>AK党官员表示，中国广汽集团与土耳其汽车制造商TOGG就电动汽车进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-gac-turkish-carmaker-togg-ev-talks-says-ak-party-official-2024-07-05/</link><description>土耳其执政党正义与发展党副主席扎菲尔·西拉卡亚 (Zafer Sirakaya) 表示，中国汽车制造商广汽集团 (GAC) 正在与土耳其电动汽车 (EV) 制造商 TOGG 就建立合资企业的可能性进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 11:57:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-gac-turkish-carmaker-togg-ev-talks-says-ak-party-official-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>国泰航空将回购香港政府剩余50%优先股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-buy-back-remaining-50-hk-governments-preference-shares-2024-07-05/</link><description>香港国泰航空周五表示，将回购7月31日向香港特别行政区政府发行的剩余50%优先股。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 11:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-buy-back-remaining-50-hk-governments-preference-shares-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国监管机构誓言严厉打击资本市场欺诈行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-regulator-vows-clamp-down-harder-capital-market-fraud-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国证券监管机构周五誓言要加大力度打击金融欺诈行为，并表示正在推动对违法者进行更严厉的惩罚，以期重振人们对中国陷入困境的股市的信心。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 11:07:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-regulator-vows-clamp-down-harder-capital-market-fraud-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>汽车制造商回应欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/carmakers-respond-eu-tariffs-chinese-made-evs-2024-07-05/</link><description>随着欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外关税于周五生效，一些汽车制造商一直在考虑是否提高价格或采取其他措施来应对。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 11:05:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/carmakers-respond-eu-tariffs-chinese-made-evs-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金 高位金价抑制印度和中国的经济活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-high-gold-prices-dull-activity-india-china-2024-07-05/</link><description>印度的实物黄金交易商因价格高企而连续第九周提供折扣，因为他们等待即将到来的预算中可能降低进口关税，而最大的消费国中国也看到需求疲软。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:51:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-high-gold-prices-dull-activity-india-china-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>蔚来首席财务官冯锋辞职，电动汽车制造商任命内部人士为继任者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nio-cfo-feng-steps-down-ev-maker-appoints-insider-successor-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车周五表示，冯伟以个人原因辞去首席财务官一职，立即生效。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nio-cfo-feng-steps-down-ev-maker-appoints-insider-successor-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：欧洲就中国老一代芯片征求行业意见</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/europe-seeks-industry-views-chinas-older-generation-chips-2024-07-05/</link><description>两位知情人士告诉路透社，欧盟委员会已开始征求该地区半导体行业对中国扩大老一代计算机芯片生产的看法。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:20:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/europe-seeks-industry-views-chinas-older-generation-chips-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：劳工焦点——美国就业、英国新政府</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-05/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:05:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪在泰国电动汽车大幅折扣引发强烈反对，总理寻求保证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byds-steep-ev-discounting-thailand-sparks-backlash-pm-seeks-assurances-2024-07-05/</link><description>自从对比亚迪经销商大幅打折行为发起调查以来，泰国消费者保护机构已收到约 70 起投诉，这让一些买家感觉自己为中国电动汽车支付了过高的价格。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 09:41:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byds-steep-ev-discounting-thailand-sparks-backlash-pm-seeks-assurances-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>上海多家中国国有企业购买特斯拉 Model Y 汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/several-chinese-state-firms-shanghai-buy-tesla-model-y-cars-2024-07-05/</link><description>当地政府周五发布声明称，中国金融中心上海的几家国有企业最近购买了特斯拉最畅销的 Model Y 作为服务车。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 09:15:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/several-chinese-state-firms-shanghai-buy-tesla-model-y-cars-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：菲律宾在南海紧张局势中拒绝美国的帮助——军事首长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-turned-down-us-help-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-military-chief-2024-07-05/</link><description>菲律宾军事参谋长表示，在与中国就在有争议的浅滩上为菲律宾军队补给的任务发生冲突后，菲律宾拒绝了美国协助其在南海行动的提议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 08:46:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-turned-down-us-help-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-military-chief-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>尽管美国制裁，中国人工智能公司在人工智能盛会上展示了韧性和创新</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-ai-firms-showcase-resilience-innovations-ai-event-despite-us-sanctions-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国的科技公司，从行业巨头到雄心勃勃的初创公司，本周齐聚上海举行的世界人工智能大会，展示他们的最新创新成果，并表达对中国人工智能行业的大力支持，尽管该行业面临美国的制裁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 08:30:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-ai-firms-showcase-resilience-innovations-ai-event-despite-us-sanctions-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>富士康第二季度营收超出人工智能服务器需求市场预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconn-q2-revenue-jumps-19-yy-sees-growth-q3-2024-07-05/</link><description>全球最大的电子产品合同制造商和苹果最大的 iPhone 组装商台湾富士康周五发布的人工智能服务器需求季度收入好于预期，并预测本季度将持续增长。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 07:38:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconn-q2-revenue-jumps-19-yy-sees-growth-q3-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>奇瑞计划在欧洲扩张，在意大利推出 28,000 欧元跨界 SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chery-launches-28000-euro-crossover-suv-italy-it-plans-europe-expansion-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国奇瑞汽车正在评估其在欧洲扩大生产能力和销售的选择，其汽油版 Omoda 5 跨界 SUV 开始在意大利销售，起价为 27,900 欧元（30,182 美元）。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 07:27:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chery-launches-28000-euro-crossover-suv-italy-it-plans-europe-expansion-2024-07-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>